# Leo Portfolio — Cursor Rules

## Typography — NEVER override these
- html { font-size: clamp(14px, 1.4vw, 20px) } is the only px font-size allowed
- All other font-sizes must be in rem
- Do not add font-size overrides inside @media blocks

## Nav
- One canonical nav.nav-pill rule lives in style.css only
- project-style.css must contain zero nav or .nav-pill rules
- Every page has <nav class="nav-pill"> with: Home | About | Research | Resume

## CSS load order
- <link> to style.css must always come before project-style.css on every page

## New project pages
- Copy the project template shell (nav + main + footer structure)
- No active class on any nav link
- Footer must match index.html exactly

## Three.js
- New computers added only via addComputerToScene(videoUrl)
- Always call fitCameraToScene() then fitBackgroundToCamera() after adding
- All video elements stored in screenVideos[] array
- All VideoTextures stored in videoTextureMap (Map keyed by video element)

## General
- Do not introduce new CSS frameworks or libraries
- Do not change file names of existing pages
- Append an entry to CHANGELOG.md after every meaningful change
